text:
Hey... What's wrong?
Is there something bothering you?

It's just that when I put on this outfit, it reminded me
of my middle school graduation ceremony...

Oh...!
Hiori, your middle school uniform was a sailor outfit, right?

Yes, just until recently I was in middle school,
so it feels nostalgic...
I thought it was something I would never wear again.
I guess you could call it fate, this kind of thing...
